| Copy various NCFresco HTML templates to STB's local store
CDir   Cache:$.NCFresco
Access Cache:$.NCFresco Lrw/r
CDir   Cache:$.NCFresco.html
Access Cache:$.NCFresco.html Lrw/r

| Get the NCFresco path set up...
If "<TV$Type>" = "NTSC"  Then Set NCFresco$Path <NCFresco$Dir>.Resources.USA.,<NCFresco$Dir>.
If "<TV$Type>" <> "NTSC" Then Set NCFresco$Path <NCFresco$Dir>.Resources.UK.,<NCFresco$Dir>.

| Copy some files into CacheFS...
Set Tmp$Path Cache:$.NCFresco.html.
Set Alias$CacheNCF IfThere NCFresco:html.%%0 Then FCopy NCFresco:html.%%0 Tmp:%%0
Set Alias$AccessNCF IfThere Tmp:%%0 Then Access Tmp:%%0 Lrw/r

CacheNCF  badurl
AccessNCF badurl
CacheNCF  favs
AccessNCF favs
CacheNCF  favsd
AccessNCF favsd
CacheNCF  hista
AccessNCF hista
CacheNCF  histr
AccessNCF histr
CacheNCF  jsalert
AccessNCF jsalert
CacheNCF  jsokcncl
AccessNCF jsokcncl
CacheNCF  jsprompt
AccessNCF jsprompt
CacheNCF  optfonts
AccessNCF optfonts
CacheNCF  opttext
AccessNCF opttext
CacheNCF  password
AccessNCF password
CacheNCF  printopts
AccessNCF printopts
CacheNCF  sslcert
AccessNCF sslcert
CacheNCF  sslpin
AccessNCF sslpin
CacheNCF  sslserv
AccessNCF sslserv
CacheNCF  ssltoken
AccessNCF ssltoken
CacheNCF  url
AccessNCF url

Unset Alias$AccessNCF
Unset Alias$CacheNCF
Unset Tmp$Path
